'''Tea Leaves''' are [[vegetables]] that are harvested from [[Tea Bush]]es each day during the last week of [[Spring]], [[Summer]], and [[Fall]] (and [[Winter]] if indoors).

Tea Leaves can be put into a [[Keg]] to make [[Green Tea]], though Pickled Tea Leaves are more profitable.

